    "This paper addresses this emerging gap by introducing LEAP (https:// ai4ph ysed. physik.",
    "uni-muenc hen.",
    "de/ LEAP/ engli sh_ examp le/ Newto ns_ pendu lum) (Learning with AI about Physics), a platform that streamlines the creation of learning content and fosters interaction with a LLM.",
    "LEAP has already been briefly introduced in various educational contexts (Avila et al., 2024; S. Küchemann et al., 2024; Steinert et al., 2024b); however, the aim of this manuscript is to explore the potential of LEAP in enhancing the learning experience and to discuss the future implications of such tools for educational practices.",
    "The development of LEAP addresses a significant research gap in the effective integration of Large Language Models (LLMs) in educational settings, particularly in the provision of formative feedback."
